Ip6wall is a project of Fabio Borraccetti <miasma@no-net.org>.
Ip6wall is has been rewritten but still there are some pieces 
of old ip6wall version that was based on a modified copy of gShield which
is written by R. Gregory <godot@linuxmafia.org>.
Second most important source of code is http://easyfwgen.morizot.net/gen/ 
automatically generated script. 
See Changelog for a list of changes.

gShield was downloaded from http://muse.linuxmafia.org/gshield.html
Upstream Author: R. Gregory <godot@linuxmafia.org>

